These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-1::.
City: liverpool, berlin, london
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to liverpool is not to the left of the person traveling to berlin##8
3. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to berlin##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3     |
| City   | london | berlin | liverpool |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-2::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, september, august
1. the person who's birthday is in august is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##8
2. the person who's birthday is in august is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3     |
| Birthday   | november | august | september |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, comedy, superhero
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person watching romance movies is not to the right of the person watching superhero movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | romance | superhero |

 #################################

 
